==========================================================================

Once everything is finally installed set the JAVA_HOME variable to
${LOCALBASE}/ where are OpenJDK or Diablo JDK installed and run
the Tomcat server.
The JetSpeed portal files are copied to ${LOCALBASE}/apache-tomcat*/webapps,
where Tomcat resides.

For more information on how it works look at JetSpeed homepage.

==========================================================================
